\section*{Activity 2.2}

Take a few drops of water from a pond．Spread on a glass slide and observe through a microscope．
Do you find tiny organisms moving around？

\section*{Activity 2.4}

Take a 500 mL beaker filled upto $\frac{3}{4}$ with water. Dissolve $2-3$ teaspoons of sugar in it. Add half a
spoon of yeast powder to the sugar solution. Keep it covered in a warm place for $4-5$ hours. Now smell the solution. Can you get a smell?
